name: Unidentified_Quarren_bounty
content: During the Galactic Civil War, a Quarren had a bounty place on their head. The bounty hunter Boba Fett tracked the Quarren to a cantina, where he captured the bounty alive, restraining them at blaster-point. The Quarren was orange-skinned with green eyes, and dressed in a white shirt with black pants and waistcoat.
